"This guide covers the basics of making a new card with a JSON file and "
"localization. This guide assumes that you've already read `The Tutorial "
"<tutorial.html>`_."
msgstr ""
"本指南介绍了使用 JSON 文件制作新卡和本地化的基本知识，并假定你已经阅读过`快速"
"入门 <Tutorial.html>`_。"

