#: ../../source/guides/golden_berry.rst:17 5bfadf97c1f249cbb6c3fc83a64d9f06
msgid "Step 1. Creating the JSON file"
msgstr "第1步：创建 JSON 文件"

#: ../../source/guides/golden_berry.rst:19 194a1078cfd94867b76a2a8afc13a413
msgid ""
"All custom cards (and ideas and packs) are created with JSON files. Let's "
"take a look at the bare minimum need to create our first card! Create a "
"``golden_berry.json`` file in the ``Cards/`` folder, and add the following "
"code:"
msgstr ""
"所有自定义卡牌（以及点子和卡包）都是用 JSON 文件创建的。让我们来看看创建我们"
"的第一张卡的最低需求！在 ``Cards/`` 文件夹中创建 ``golden_berry.json`` 文件，"
"并添加以下代码："

#: ../../source/guides/golden_berry.rst:31 35f2d4b832464f9a8b6cb274694ece73
msgid ""
"``id`` is the cards ID. This must be a unique string, so it's highly "
"recommended to prefix it with your mods ID! ``nameTerm`` and "
"``descriptionTerm`` are terms (see the `Localization <localization.html>`_ "
"section for more info) for the cards name and description respectively. You "
"should use terms whenever possible, but you can choose to use "
"``nameOverride`` or ``descriptionOverride`` for quickly trying things out."
msgstr ""
"``id`` 是这张卡片的 ID。这必须是一个独特的字符串，所以我们推荐是用你的 MOD "
"的 ID 作为它的前缀！``nameTerm`` 和 ``descriptionTerm`` 是这张卡牌的名称与描"
"述的本地化表达键（参考`本地化 <localization.html>`_章节以获取更多信息）。在任"
"何时候都应该使用本地化键，但是你可以在开发时使用 ``nameOverride`` 或 "
"``descriptionOverride`` 以快速测试。"

#: ../../source/guides/golden_berry.rst:37 1cb44051f0bb4f42846b2c3b39b1d72d
msgid "Step 2. Testing the mod"
msgstr "第2步：测试 MOD"

#: ../../source/guides/golden_berry.rst:39 db1325a683b340a09cfcb56f44a48f51
msgid ""
"Let's run a quick test to make sure everything is working! Simply run the "
"``build.py`` script (ideally from a terminal), and if everything went right, "
"you should see a similar output:"
msgstr ""
"让我们进行一个快速测试，以确保一切正常！只需运行 ``build.py`` 脚本（需要已经"
"安装了 Python 环境，并且最好是从终端），如果一切顺利，应该会看到类似的输出："

#: ../../source/guides/golden_berry.rst:48 867c18b16d554c28b2b37ec727a72fa7
msgid ""
"If you set up everything correctly, you should now see your mod in game! You "
"can verify it's loaded by checking the Mods menu:"
msgstr ""
"如果你设置正确，你现在应该在游戏中看到你的 mod 了！可以通过检查 Mods 菜单来验"
"证它是否已加载："

#: ../../source/guides/golden_berry.rst:52 3613cac51fe6433da32904dafe687330
msgid ""
"If you can see the mod, that likely means your card is loaded too. While in "
"a run, you can open the debug menu by holding the K and O keys and pressing "
"F1. Head to the \"Cards\" tab and search for the Golden Berry card, and "
"click the text to spawn it!"
msgstr ""
"如果你能看到mod，那可能意味着你的卡牌也被加载了。在运行过程中，您可以通过按住"
"K和O键并按F1打开调试菜单。前往“卡牌”选项卡，搜索 Golden Berry，然后点击文本生"
"成它！"

#: ../../source/guides/golden_berry.rst:58 b9bb9da46f924b75ac45af67401319d3
msgid ""
"If your card doesn't show up in the debug menu, there could be a few things "
"going wrong:"
msgstr "如果您的卡牌没有显示在调试菜单中，可能是由于以下问题："

#: ../../source/guides/golden_berry.rst:60 483b247b83354b309ba143d6f34ced72
msgid ""
"If the mod is crossed out in the Mods menu, that means it's disabled. Enable "
"it by clicking the \"Disable/Enable Mods\" button at the bottom of the Mods "
"screen."
msgstr ""
"如果 mod 在 Mods 菜单中被划掉，那就意味着它被禁用了。通过单击 Mods 页面底部"
"的“Disable/Enable Mods”（禁用/启用 Mods）按钮启用它。"

#: ../../source/guides/golden_berry.rst:61 8c08db7304bb4eed847bf896d80155dd
msgid ""
"If the card name shows up as ``---MISSING---`` in the debug menu, the "
"localization.tsv file didn't get copied correctly."
msgstr ""
"如果卡牌名在调试菜单中显示为 ``---MISSING---``，则说明 ``localization.tsv`` 文件没有被正确复制。"

#: ../../source/guides/golden_berry.rst:64 81690fafc0854fc1b2a057634c4156e4
msgid "Step 3. Making the card useful"
msgstr "第3步：让卡牌变得有用"

#: ../../source/guides/golden_berry.rst:66 47745782c210495b8985684a55728217
msgid "But first, let's make it look a bit nicer:"
msgstr "首先，我们先让它看上去好看一点："

#: ../../source/guides/golden_berry.rst:79 81a393cadc654153b00b839cf4445b44
msgid ""
"``icon`` is the cards icon. This may be a PNG file in the Images folder of "
"your mod (such as \"Example.png\"), or the ID of a card. If you provide a "
"card ID, the icon will be \"borrowed\" from that card. ``value`` is the "
"value of your card, you may set this to -1 if you want the card to be "
"unsellable. Don't forget to build your mod after making changes to the JSON "
"file!"
msgstr ""
"``icon`` 代表这个卡牌的图标。这可以是一个位于你的图片文件夹中的 PNG 文件（例"
"如 ``Example.png``）或者一个其他卡牌的 ID。如果你使用一个卡牌 ID，那么这张卡"
"牌的图标将会与 ID 对应的卡牌一样。``value`` 是你的卡牌的价值，可以将这一条目"
"设置为 -1 如果你想让卡牌不可出售。不要忘了在对 JSON 文件作出修改后重新构建你"
"的模组！"

#: ../../source/guides/golden_berry.rst:83 3d83dbc8db9c4739b206b0d39ef4c943
msgid "Our golden berry now looks like a berry, and can be sold for 10 gold."
msgstr "我们的金浆果现在看上去跟浆果一样，然后可以卖出10个金币。"

#: ../../source/guides/golden_berry.rst:87 fce0749da3794a10b5ca3223f666ce8c
msgid ""
"Now, we will turn it into a food that our villagers can consume. We can add "
"functionality to our card with the ``script`` property, where the value may "
"be the name of any class that extends ``CardData``. In our case, this will "
"be the ``Food`` class. We will also need to set the ``type`` of our card to "
"``Food``."
msgstr ""
"现在，我们会把它变成一个我们的村民可以食用的食物。我们可以使用 ``script`` 属"
"性为我们的卡牌添加功能，其值可以是任何继承了 ``CardData`` 的类名。在我们这"
"里，这应该是 ``Food`` 类。我们同时应该将 ``type`` 属性设置为 ``Food``。"

#: ../../source/guides/golden_berry.rst:106 1197edd810a8470888560524a93175a5
msgid ""
"Our card now looks like any other food card (and can be stacked on them)! "
"Villagers can also consume it, however it's only worth 1 food point. For "
"further functionality, we will need to use :raw-html:`<u>Underscore "
"Properties</u>`."
msgstr ""
"我们的卡牌现在看上去和其他任何食物卡牌一样（同时也可以与他们堆叠在一起）！村"
"民也可以食用它们，虽然它只能提供1点食物。为了实现更多功能，我们需要食用 :raw-"
"html:`<u>下划线属性</u>`。"

#: ../../source/guides/golden_berry.rst:109 e688870d445a4d13b41c6f4947ddbac7
msgid ""
"Underscore Properties are any key which starts with an underscore (_). The "
"available properties depend on the selected script. All public fields in the "
"classes are available as underscore properties. If you `decompiled the game "
"<decompiling.html>`_, you can easily take a look at them. Let's take a look "
"at the code of the ``Food`` class! We can find the ``Food`` class in "
"``GameScripts.dll``, alongside all the base game code."
msgstr ""
"下划线属性代表由下划线（_）开头的任何键。可选的属性值取决于你所使用的脚本类"
"型。所有公开字段都可以作为下划线属性使用。如果你已经 `反编译 <decompiling."
"html>`_了游戏，你可以轻松地看到它们。让我们看一看 ``Food`` 类的代码！我们可以"
"在 ``GameScripts.dll`` 中找到 ``Food`` 类，和其他游戏底层代码一起。"

#: ../../source/guides/golden_berry.rst:116 4cf89f2e71fa43a88d7bab5026a24caa
msgid ""
"We can see a ``FoodValue`` field, and if we do some further digging into the "
"code, we can figure out that this holds the food points of a food card. If "
"we want to set this value in a JSON file, we can simply prefix the field "
"name with an underscore, like so: ``\"_FoodValue\": 10``. In the screenshot "
"we can also see a ``CanSpoil`` field, so let's set that to false."
msgstr ""
"我们可以看到一个 ``FoodValue`` 字段，如果我们进一步深入代码，我们可以发现这个"
"字段控制一个食物卡的食物点数。如果我们想要在 JSON 文件中配置这个值，我们只需"
"要在字段名前面加上一个下换线，像这样：``\"_FoodValue\": 10``。在这个截图中我"
"们也可以看到一个 ``CanSpoil`` 字段，让我们把它设置为 ``false``。"

#: ../../source/guides/golden_berry.rst:135 2f4f88b382d44bd8887d822346ea96cb
msgid ""
"If we spawn a new Golden Berry card, we can see it has 10 food points and "
"will no longer spoil on the island."
msgstr ""
"如果我们现在创建一个新的 Golden Berry 卡牌，我们可以看到它有10点食物点并且在"
"岛屿上不会腐烂。"

#: ../../source/guides/golden_berry.rst:138 04789151d3224ed0b42134ad354211dc
msgid "Step 4. Making the card pretty"
msgstr "第4步：美化卡牌"

#: ../../source/guides/golden_berry.rst:140 b5381d1953194deea81f627ad7e77483
msgid ""
"We can also specify a custom color palette in the JSON to change how the "
"card looks. These are done with the ``_HasUniquePalette`` and ``_MyPalette`` "
"underscore properties."
msgstr ""
"我们还可以在JSON中指定一个自定义调色板来更改卡片的外观。这些都是通过配置 "
"``_HasUniquePalette`` 和 ``_MyPalette`` 下划线属性完成的。"

#: ../../source/guides/golden_berry.rst:164 55664171a67642ae951adb9323562caa
msgid ""
"The colors in ``_MyPalette`` are hex colors. We can also add ``\"_IsShiny\": "
"true`` to make the card shiny like a coin. Our final card will look like so:"
msgstr ""
"在 ``_MyPalette`` 中使用的颜色是十六进制颜色。我们也可以添加 ``\"_IsShiny\": "
"true`` 来让这个卡变得金光闪闪，就像金币一样。我们的最终成果将会像这样："

#: ../../source/guides/golden_berry.rst:170 137b3d1c257d42c9915ac393db2c8574
msgid "Step 5. Creating the idea"
msgstr "第5步：创建一个点子"

#: ../../source/guides/golden_berry.rst:172 995b94fe53a94f00b1c74270df0444c8
msgid ""
"If we want players to know how to make a Golden Berry, we need to tell them "
"with an idea card. Idea cards are also created as JSON files in the "
"``Blueprints/`` folder. Create a file called ``golden_berry_idea.json`` in "
"the folder, and add the following code:"
msgstr ""
"如果我们想让玩家知道如何制作 Golden Berry，我们需要用一张点子卡牌来告诉他们。"
"创意卡也是通过 ``Blueprints/`` 文件夹中的 JSON 文件进行创建和配置。在文件夹中"
"创建一个名为 ``golden_berry_idea.json`` 的文件，并添加以下代码："

#: ../../source/guides/golden_berry.rst:184 2568ecbd7a5a43aba1e6648ac15b0216
msgid ""
"Don't build your mod just yet, as this will cause errors! The blueprint "
"needs to specify one or more :raw-html:`<u>subprints</u>`. Subprints are "
"what actually hold the \"recipe\" for a card. Many blueprints in the base "
"game (such as Blueprint_Growth) hold dozens of subprints."
msgstr ""
"现在还不要构建你的模组，因为它会出错！蓝图需要指定至少一个 :raw-html:"
"`<u>subprints</u>`。子蓝图（subprints）才真正控制一张卡牌的配方。许多游戏中的"
"蓝图都有大量的子蓝图（例如 ``Blueprint_Growth``）。"

#: ../../source/guides/golden_berry.rst:205 94d0775b9e244c6692601287aa337487
msgid ""
"A subprint object needs to specify 4 things (at least): the required cards "
"(seperated by a comma), a result card, the time it will take (in seconds), "
"and a text for the status. We can now spawn the idea card from the debug "
"menu, and it will also show up in the Ideas menu."
msgstr ""
"子打印对象需要指定4件事（至少）：所需卡牌（用逗号分隔）、产出卡牌、所需时间"
"（以秒为单位）和状态文本。我们现在可以从调试菜单中生成点子卡，它也将显示在点"
"子菜单中。"

#: ../../source/guides/golden_berry.rst:214 d2d32b00488042a2b1e03dd75e14a925
msgid "Step 6. Adding the idea to packs"
msgstr "第6步：将点子添加到卡牌包"

#: ../../source/guides/golden_berry.rst:216 ece48c80b5e24a92a5c9f608379f074e
msgid ""
"To make sure the idea card is available in card packs, we need to write a "
"bit of code. In the ``Ready`` method of your ``Mod`` class, add the "
"following line of code:"
msgstr ""
"为了确保点子卡在卡牌包中可用，我们需要写一小点代码。在你的 ``Mod`` 类的 "
"``Ready`` 方法中，添加以下代码："

#: ../../source/guides/golden_berry.rst:224 5ef6b7bce7f9459b98f15b7dedb8a774
msgid ""
"This will add the blueprint to the CookingIdea set card bag (with a weight "
"of 1, same as every other card in the bag), so it will appear in the Curious "
"Cuisine pack (as long as the idea hasn't been discovered yet)."
msgstr ""
"这将把蓝图添加到 ``CookingIdea`` 集合中（权重为1，与包中的其他卡相同），因此"
"它将出现在 ``Curious Cuisine`` 卡包中（只要这个点子还没有被发现）。"
